headline: 1 Industrials Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Still, their generally high capital requirements expose them to the ups and downs of economic cycles, and the industry’s six-month return of 9.8% has fallen short of the S&P 500’s 13% rise.
